CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Entrada Therapeutics Inc mission is to transform the treatment of devastating diseases and improve patients quality of life by developing intracellular biologics. Leveraging its proprietary Endosomal Escape Vehicle platform, Entrada is creating a diverse and expanding pipeline of oligonucleotide, antibody, enzyme, protein and peptide programs to efficiently target and engage underlying drivers of diseases.
